+/* Verification was four independent round trips: bump the counter, update the
+   payment, write the public receipt, log it. Lose the connection between any
+   two and the society is left with a payment marked verified whose printed QR
+   resolves to "receipt not found" — or a burned receipt number and no receipt.
+   The payment record and its public counterpart now commit as one write.
+
